metadata.name: Total Cyborg Museum
metadata.description:
At all times, the magnificent profiles of beauties was sculpted in stone. Art of portraiture will not disappear, with the advent of technology. Everywhere in the universe (even in famous museums) digital beauties will stonewall the viewer with their piercing gaze. But now beauty doesn't kill, JETLAG knows a way to turn a museum piece on and off.

Inscription on the label: Museum exhibit "Cyborg Gorgon Μέδουσα" turn on by pressing the lever with two red buttons.

7000x7000 pix

artists @danitta_push, @KLAWMACHINE
